calculateArea(width, height)#

Calculates the area of a rectangle.

参数:

  • width (number) – The width of the rectangle.

  • height (number) – The height of the rectangle.

返回:

number – The area of the rectangle.

Examples:

// Example usage:
// Returns 20
const area = calculateArea(4, 5);
AndroidBotMain.any_elements_exists(xpath_list: List[str], wait_time: float = None, interval_time: float = None) → Optional[str]#

遍历列表中的元素，只要任意一个元素存在就返回 True

参数:

  • xpath_list – xpath 列表

  • wait_time – 等待时间，默认取 self.wait_timeout

  • interval_time – 轮询间隔时间，默认取 self.interval_timeout

返回:

任意一个元素存在就返回 True
